Rating: 4
I first experienced this salad in Capri, Italy (called Insalata Caprese) and longed for it when I got back to the States. So far this is the best version I have found. As other reviewers have mentioned, use fresh mozzarella - the prepackaged mozzarella in the cheese section just won't do. I also loved the high vinegar content; balsamic vinegar is just sooo good, why taint it with oil? Don't skimp on the basil - it adds so much flavor.

Rating: 4
